1
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,320
It's all up to you in a bit.

2
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:59,159
Exchange the Birth Characters.

3
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,519
Let me do it.

4
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:11,000
Okay, okay, okay.

5
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:14,239
Where's your card?

6
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,040
Right here, right here.

7
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,760
Hand it over.

8
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:34,640
Sorceress.

9
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:36,519
Is something wrong with this?

10
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:38,319
It's nothing.

11
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:39,680
With this,

12
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,480
I can report to the Brigade Commander.

13
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,640
Let's go.

14
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,680
Take care now.

15
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:45,439
Let's go.

16
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,120
Right now.

17
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,920
We're off.

18
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:53,719
You two.

19
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,480
Take care.

20
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,760
Brother-in-law, this...

21
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,640
Qiuying.

22
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,280
Qiuying.

23
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:05,200
I'm so sorry, my child.

24
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,640
But I'm only doing this

25
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,280
for your own good, Qiuying.

26
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,520
Such a vast family fortune,

27
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,759
I can't let it crumble in my hands.

28
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:18,879
My heart aches too.

29
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:20,080
Qiuying.

30
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,919
Can you forgive me?

31
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,319
You all go on ahead.

32
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,360
I need to use the restroom.

33
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,879
Still mad at me?

34
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,800
What did you promise me earlier?

35
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,520
Don't worry.

36
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,159
The Brigade Commander's son

37
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:48,080
won't live past seven days.

38
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,080
What?

39
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,719
You peed on my shoe!

40
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,240
Wait,

41
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,240
did you put a curse on him?

42
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,960
You wouldn't be that ruthless, would you?

43
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,280
Of course not.

44
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,759
I'm from a righteous sect.

45
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,360
He brought it on himself.

46
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,800
What do you mean?

47
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,360
Judging from his Pulse condition,

48
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,319
his pulse is weak,

49
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,120
hollow when pressed,

50
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,800
choppy in flow,

51
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,479
like a blade scraping bamboo.

52
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,240
The pulse is thin as a thread.

53
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,280
That's a choppy pulse,

54
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:10,919
a hollow pulse,

55
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:11,680
and a thready pulse.

56
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:14,080
Plus, he has festering sores.

57
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:14,560
Hold on,

58
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,319
can you say

59
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:16,599
something I can actually understand?

60
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,360
It's late-stage syphilis.

61
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:21,400
Look at his face,

62
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,280
painted snow white,

63
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,000
just to hide the sores.

64
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:26,159
And he's been smoking opium for ages.

65
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:27,680
I said seven days,

66
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:29,080
but that's even being generous.

67
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:32,280
No way.

68
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,439
Qiuying absolutely cannot

69
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,280
marry someone like that.

70
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:37,479
Don't worry.

71
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:38,599
Just hold on a few more days.

72
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,120
Got it.

73
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,319
Let's go.

74
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,080
You're not lying to me, right?

75
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,360
I'm not.

76
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,680
Next time, aim better.

77
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:53,919
I did that on purpose.

78
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,800
I've only been gone a few days.

79
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,400
How did it get this bad?

80
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:15,919
Forget it.

81
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:17,839
If I can't save my son,

82
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,680
I have to save my grandson.

83
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:20,920
Shuisheng.

84
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:21,680
Yes, sir.

85
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,040
Go to the mayor's house.

86
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,759
Bring back the mayor's daughter.

87
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:26,759
The wedding is tomorrow.

88
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:28,959
What's with the "huh"?

89
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:29,720
Hurry.

90
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,120
But what if

91
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:32,120
the mayor's family refuses?

92
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,439
Is that a fire poker

93
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:36,399
tucked in your belt?

94
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,480
Get going.

95
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:39,399
Yes, sir.

96
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,319
Move out.

97
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,639
Sorceress.

98
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,040
My son,

99
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:47,160
is there any way

100
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:48,959
to bring him back from the dead?

101
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,079
I'm not marrying him, end of story.

102
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,160
Niece...

103
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:17,079
You're just talking out of anger.

104
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:19,199
We've already accepted the betrothal gifts.

105
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:19,680
That's right.

106
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,399
Mother,

107
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:26,560
I hear the Brigade Commander's son

108
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:28,079
hangs out at brothels every day,

109
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,839
smokes opium,

110
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:30,240
and even has a venereal disease.

111
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,759
How can you bear

112
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:33,519
to push your daughter into that hellhole?

113
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,399
What?

114
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:36,319
Husband,

115
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,240
you must

116
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,600
call off this marriage right away.

117
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,680
Marriage is no trifling matter.

118
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,839
You can't just call it off on a whim.

119
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,560
He's the Brigade Commander's son.

120
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,199
If we upset them in any way,

121
00:05:45,319 --> 00:05:46,120
our whole family...

122
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:48,879
Sister.

123
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:50,360
Brother-in-law is right.

124
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,399
Those commoners are just

125
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:53,519
jealous of this match,

126
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:54,759
so they spread rumors out there.

127
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,959
How could we possibly believe them?

128
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,079
Besides,

129
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,480
I think

130
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,879
the Brigade Commander's son

131
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,000
is actually pretty handsome.

132
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,319
I don't care.

133
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,480
I'm not marrying him, no matter what.

134
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,759
If you want to marry him, you marry him.

135
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,720
Master!

136
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:10,319
Over here.

137
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,000
Master,

138
00:06:12,079 --> 00:06:13,000
something terrible has happened!

139
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:14,360
The Brigade Commander has sent men over.

140
00:06:14,439 --> 00:06:15,120
What for?

141
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:16,959
To pick up the young miss.

142
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,639
They say the wedding is tonight.

143
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:19,839
What?

144
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,199
Wasn't it agreed the wedding

145
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:22,079
would be on the 15th of this month?

146
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:23,600
You'll have to ask the Brigade Commander.

147
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,319
Please, miss, get in the car.

148
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,120
Listen, Captain Shui,

149
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,480
look at the time.

150
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,480
If we miss the auspicious hour,

151
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,319
that wouldn't be good.

152
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,959
She's been ready for a while now.

153
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,000
And you, child,

154
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,240
you bring gifts every time you come.

155
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:37,839
I don't need them.

156
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:38,759
I have everything I need.

157
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,560
Put them away.

158
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:41,079
Come here, my daughter.

159
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:42,560
On such a joyous day,

160
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,560
let's have no tears.

161
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,079
Just live a good life together.

162
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,240
Won't you?

163
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:48,000
Go on.

164
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:49,560
My daughter.

165
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,040
My dear girl,

166
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,600
be happy.

167
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:54,879
I can't bear to let you go.

168
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,079
I can't bear it, I can't bear it.

169
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,040
I'm just following orders.

170
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,079
Please forgive me.

171
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,360
You all step outside for now.

172
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,120
Yes, sir.

173
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,600
Go on,

174
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,879
say what you have to say.

175
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,160
Qiuying,

176
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,680
I will never let you

177
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,519
marry that scumbag.

178
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,720
You're just a soldier.

179
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:31,800
You can't fight someone that powerful.

180
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:33,399
What can you possibly do?

181
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,959
At worst, we'll go down fighting.

182
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:36,759
Shuisheng,

183
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,800
don't you dare do anything foolish.

184
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:56,800
Qiuying,

185
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,319
don't worry.

186
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,160
I have an expert guiding me.

187
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,959
He said we'll definitely

188
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:02,759
grow old together.

189
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:06,759
Don't cry.

190
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:09,879
I'll head out now.

191
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,240
Stay safe.

192
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:29,000
Why were you eavesdropping?

193
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,920
I never said

194
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,839
you two would grow old together.

195
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:37,279
And I never said you were the expert.

196
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:42,279
You think you're funny?

197
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,039
Report.

198
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,480
Brigade Commander.

199
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:48,720
They've already

200
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,600
started preparing on Qiuying's end.

201
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:53,360
Sor...

202
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:53,960
Sorceress.

203
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:54,399
How...

204
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,519
How is he?

205
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,960
The lamp's run dry.

206
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,000
Run...

207
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:00,799
Run dry...

208
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:06,879
Run dry...

209
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,519
Run...

210
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,120
The lamp's run dry.

211
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:13,919
Go.

212
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,200
Fetch the opium.

213
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,919
I'll let him smoke his fill.

214
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,480
I don't care.

215
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,639
Before he dies,

216
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:22,960
he must leave

217
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,399
an heir for the Li family.

218
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:25,960
An heir!

219
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,120
Boil three bowls down to one.

220
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:31,960
That's all we can do.

221
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,679
Quick!

222
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:38,240
Quick!

223
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:43,320
Dongzi.

224
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,480
Let me see.

225
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:46,120
What kind of medicine is this?

226
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,000
You're taking this?

227
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,600
Not me.

228
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:52,840
It's for the Brigade Commander's son.

229
00:09:54,039 --> 00:09:54,840
I knew it.

230
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,799
You're not that weak.

231
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,639
Hurry, take a look.

232
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:58,600
I have.

233
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,039
These are all aphrodisiacs.

234
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,840
Forget that sickly guy,

235
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,919
even a healthy man would be ruined.

236
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,279
That wicked sorceress!

237
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,960
She's pushing Qiuying to her death.

238
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,519
Don't worry.

239
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,679
You go see Qiuying.

240
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,320
Leave this to me.

241
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:16,840
Dongsheng.

242
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:19,720
Thank you.

243
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,559
What a stroke of luck.

244
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,840
We get to share in the joy too.

245
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,039
Can we really do this?

246
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:37,000
Of course we can.

247
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,440
I heard

248
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,559
that sickly guy

249
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:41,720
won't make it through tonight.

250
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,000
So tell me,

251
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,960
with such

252
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,759
a beautiful young bride,

253
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:49,919
why on earth

254
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:51,759
won't he touch her?

255
00:10:52,279 --> 00:10:53,879
Isn't that perfect?

256
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:55,720
Leaves her right to us.

257
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:57,919
If the Brigade Commander finds out,

258
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,639
he'll skin us alive.

259
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:01,000
You don't know shit.

260
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,080
To die beneath the peony blossoms,

261
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:05,440
is to be a romantic ghost.

262
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,679
Shuisheng?

263
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:31,919
Is that you?

264
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,759
We're not Shuisheng.

265
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,919
We're here to help you bear a child.

266
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,360
Who are you?

267
00:11:39,399 --> 00:11:40,200
What do you want?

268
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,080
Let me introduce us.

269
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,279
I'm Xunhua.

270
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,639
He's Wenliu.

271
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:45,559
What do you think we'll do?

272
00:11:46,159 --> 00:11:47,000
Stay back!

273
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,000
Let go of me!
